title: cryptoorders
author: cryptoorders
content: I need a blockchain developer to update some information about a token on GIThub.We want to make a listing on the Valora wallet and it is necessary to open a Pull Request in which to add the token logo and some other information, according to the description below:https://github.com/valora-inc/address-metadata/blob/main/README.mdIt's an very easy task, i can offer paymenth in BSC, BNB, etcPlease contact me on telegram : https://t.me/Ambassador000

comments.author: blockman
comments.body: Post this on reddit r/bitcoin4jobs and you might find the developer you need or with the other freelance marketplaces like upwork or fiverr.
